rows.label: qev031203_MSG0001
rows.name: Do not be afraid. I will keep you safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031203_MSG0003
rows.name: It is all part of Leroy I love.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031203_MSG0004
rows.name:
...Hmm? Who are you?
We are busy. Leave us be.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031203_MSG1001
rows.name:
Everything will work out if I get ringstone
and sapphire horns from xiphias.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031203_MSG1002
rows.name:
Get them. Bring them to me.
Then I will speak with my father.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031203_MSG2001
rows.name: Father must accept Leroy once we marry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031203_MSG2002
rows.name:
My father is soft with me. He will not cast me out.
Even if I marry Earth alien.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031203_MSG2003
rows.name:
I know my father will accept Leroy as son.
But I wish we did not have to resort to such tactics.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031203_MSG3001
rows.name: I miss Leroy. But I am not worried.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031203_MSG3002
rows.name:
He will come for me. Make me happy Prone woman
for all my days.[ST:wait ]
